Struggling with clogged pores and horrid, stubborn, rough texture on your cheeks and tzone ?

Well I’ve Been using the Paula’s Choice 2% BHA Liquid Exfoliant consistently for a few weeks now and here’s what I’ve actually noticed:

🫧 Texture: It’s super watery and lightweight — no stickiness, no greasy layer. I apply it on bare skin with my fingertips or a cotton pad 

🧼 Results: It doesn’t show instant magic, but over time my skin started looking smoother, especially around the T-zone. The bumpy feel is way less.

🕳️ Pores: Definitely looks more refined now. It’s honestly amazing. 

🌸 No irritation: I was scared of purging, but thankfully didn’t face any breakouts.

Just start slow (I began with 2x a week) but now I use it every single day.

💧 No fragrance, no nonsense: Feels like skincare, not perfume — which I love.

This product has earned its right in my daily routine.

And btw …. Paula’s Choice is launching in Nykaa on the 14th of June. How exciting is that ! Cause I love ALL their products
